OL,3,CMother of woman murdered by boyfriend
OL,4,Cin his home calls for tougher sentences
OL,6,FThe mother of a woman murdered in her
OL,7,Fboyfriend's apartment in Manchester is
OL,8,Fcalling for tougher sentences for
OL,9,Fdomestic homicides.
OL,11,FElli O'Brien, who was 22, was fatally
OL,12,Fstabbed by her partner Kevin Mannion,
OL,13,F45, on August 16, 2022 in his
OL,14,FManchester city centre apartment.
OL,16,FDuring the three-week trial, Liverpool
OL,17,FCrown Court heard how Mannion killed
OL,18,FMiss O'Brien after committing several
OL,19,Fassaults on her throughout their eight-
OL,20,Fmonth relationship.
