OL,6,FShe had complained to police
OL,7,Fpreviously about being a victim of
OL,8,Fdomestic abuse, but was too frightened
OL,9,Fto name Mannion as the perpetrator.
OL,11,FMannion told the court he had no idea
OL,12,Fhow his partner had been injured, and
OL,13,Finsisted he had found her lying in the
OL,14,Fhallway outside the flat before
OL,15,Fgetting help.
