OL,3,CMother of woman murdered by boyfriend
OL,4,Cin his home calls for tougher sentences
OL,6,FOn 9 March, Mannion was jailed for
OL,7,Flife and ordered to serve a minimum
OL,8,Fterm of just over 23 years and nine
OL,9,Fmonths.
OL,11,FMiss O'Brien's mother Gail Smith has
OL,12,Fjoined families of other murdered
OL,13,Fwomen to call for an urgent review of
OL,14,Fthe sentencing guidelines for men who
OL,15,Fkill their current or former partners
OL,16,Fat home.
OL,18,FIn the UK, perpetrators can face a
OL,19,Fminimum of 15 years if they kill
OL,20,Fsomeone inside a home with a weapon
OL,21,Fthat was already there.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
