OL,6,FIf the weapon was taken to the scene
OL,7,For if the murder was committed outside
OL,8,Fa home, then the tariff changes to 10
OL,9,Fyears more, starting at 25 years.
OL,11,FDespite Mannion receiving a sentence
OL,12,Fthat was on the higher side, Gail
OL,13,Ffeels that the guidelines should
OL,14,Fchange.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
