OL,3,CMother of woman murdered by boyfriend
OL,4,Cin his home calls for tougher sentences
OL,6,FShe said: "What we say is, it's a
OL,7,Fsimple, it's easy and a non-party
OL,8,Fpolitical issue. It is an issue that
OL,9,Fneeds addressing and that sentencing
OL,10,Fstart point needs to be raised, it
OL,11,Fneeds to be shown that the value of a
OL,12,Fwoman's life is the same as that of a
OL,13,Fman's life."
OL,15,FGail says the current guidelines give
OL,16,Foff the message that killing someone
OL,17,Fin their own home is less important
OL,18,Fthan someone who was killed outside of
OL,19,Ftheir home.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
