OL,3,CMother of woman murdered by boyfriend
OL,4,Cin his home calls for tougher sentences
OL,6,FGail said: "It simply gives out as a
OL,7,Fmessage that somewhat it is less
OL,8,Fserious to stab someone in the
OL,9,Fsanctuary of their own home, somewhere
OL,10,Fthey feel safe, that is less serious.
OL,12,F"That is what is says, you are not as
OL,13,Fimportant as that life lost on the
OL,14,Fstreet.
OL,16,F"Any life lost, particularly in knife
OL,17,Fcrime is horrendous. But to say that
OL,18,Fthis is less serious because you are
OL,19,Fin own house and the knife is from
OL,20,Fyour own knife block is simply a
OL,21,Fnonsense."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
