OL,6,FGail and the other families created
OL,7,Fblack and blue plaques to signify
OL,8,Fabuse and violence.
OL,10,FThey are were designed this way to
OL,11,Fmimic the blue heritage plaques. They
OL,12,Fwere placed onto buildings to
OL,13,Femphasise that a person had been
OL,14,Fkilled in a home and to say murder is
OL,15,Fmurder, in a bid to change the law.
OL,17,FITV News Granada have approached the
OL,18,FMinistry of Justice but are yet to
OL,19,Freceive a response.
